Starscream

Starscram thoguth. Terrorsaur would be a good leader, but there was a 
problem.

"We've got a conflict of interest here. Terrorsaur wants to go with 
the Preds, but KitKat's last order was for us to go with the 
alliance. Personally I would choose the Alliance because of how they 
saved us, but it is not my decision to make. So now what do we do? 
Ket KitKat's last order stand or take Terrorsaur's first?"
______________________________________________________________________
Brix

Brix pondered.

"Well......I think I can do it. It can't be so hard. Put you in 
stasis lock, open up your chest plate. Carefully remove your spark, 
remove Fliq's plate, and place it inside. Than your job would happen. 
When you're done take control of Fliq's body and tell me."
